    </statement>
    <statement id="526.txt-2">
      <text>Outer phyllaries rarely purple-spotted , linear to lanceolate or deltate, smallest 0.5–2.5 mm wide, apices (erect) acute to acuminate, abaxial faces often scurfy-puberulent and black-villous.</text>
